      • overflow

        public java.lang.String overflow
        How to handle the annotation's label that flow outside the plot area. The justify option aligns the label inside the plot area. demo: https://jsfiddle.net/gh/get/library/pure/highcharts/highcharts/tree/master/samples/highcharts/annotations/label-crop-overflow/ : Crop or justify labels accepted values: ["none", "justify"]

      • formatter

        public HIFunction formatter
        Callback JavaScript function to format the annotation's label. Note that if a format or text are defined, the format or text take precedence and the formatter is ignored. This refers to a point object. demo: https://jsfiddle.net/gh/get/library/pure/highcharts/highcharts/tree/master/samples/highcharts/annotations/label-text/ : Set labels text default: function () { return defined(this.y) ? this.y : 'Annotation label'; }
